1
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,840
♪The world decays, in gloom I stray♪

2
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,900
♪Right and wrong, in frost engraved♪

3
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:32,750
♪On dreams of love, blades clash and sway♪

4
00:00:36,590 --> 00:00:39,240
♪Alone I ride, blood still unswayed♪

5
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:42,370
♪Through heaven's mirth and earth's despair♪

6
00:00:42,930 --> 00:00:48,370
♪Toasting the moon, I drink the chill air♪

7
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,800
♪Though hearts like battlefields may be♪

8
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:55,300
♪Let fate write its uncertainty♪

9
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:58,480
♪From this life to the great unknown♪

10
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:05,150
♪Who'll stand with me, on thrones unknown?♪

11
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:10,400
♪I'll wander through this life to guard you♪

12
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:13,660
♪Through mortal realms, serene I roam♪

13
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:17,520
♪With you, the world becomes my home♪

14
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:21,400
♪Unbroken, bold, as I have sworn♪

15
00:01:21,580 --> 00:01:25,970
♪I'll roam this life, and feel no torn♪

16
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:29,320
♪Our souls embraced, no regret born♪

17
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:33,100
♪By twilight's lamp, though night be worn♪

18
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:36,750
♪Through deepest dark, I'll find the morn♪

19
00:01:36,750 --> 00:01:40,990
=Fight For Love=

20
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,940
=Episode 9=

21
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:04,910
Relax.

22
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:05,910
No one else is here,

23
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:07,120
just you and me.

24
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,480
In broad daylight?

25
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,760
- That's not appropriate.
- Come on.

26
00:02:10,950 --> 00:02:12,000
You bad boy.

27
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,120
Yun, Lady Yu.

28
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,180
- Listen.
- You're so bad.

29
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,040
We would never...

30
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:24,630
We would never

31
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:25,630
stoop to eavesdropping.

32
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,590
Why?

33
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,230
Don't you want the Crown Prince?

34
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,430
He's inside.

35
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,080
- Listen.
- Come catch me.

36
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:34,920
Hurry.

37
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,150
Come on.

38
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,080
Got you.

39
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:41,550
You cheated.

40
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,960
No one will find out, right?

41
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:45,990
It's just us.

42
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:46,990
Really?

43
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,360
Don't run.

44
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,470
Don't be shy.

45
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,190
Stop it.

46
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,150
What are you doing?

47
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,590
Just what you're thinking.

48
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:01,310
You knew this all along?

49
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,280
The Crown Prince is engaged

50
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,120
to our Tuantuan.

51
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,310
So of course I bribed an

52
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,680
Eastern Palace eunuch to keep an eye on him.

53
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,470
He even bought a dancer

54
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,750
from Fragrance House the other day.

55
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,840
I paid a lot of silver

56
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,710
for that information.

57
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,080
I was about to talk to him.

58
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,400
And since you happened to need him,

59
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:26,750
perfect.

60
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,840
Two birds with one stone.

61
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,400
What two birds with one

62
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,870
stone?

63
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:38,310
You just want me to help you

64
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,150
catch him cheating.

65
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,750
But didn't I help you

66
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:41,590
find him?

67
00:03:42,090 --> 00:03:42,960
And you said

68
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,910
going straight to

69
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,030
the Eastern Palace would look bad.

70
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,080
I only knew he'd be here.

71
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,150
I must've been crazy

72
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,000
to ask for your help.

73
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,400
But I did help, didn't I?

74
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,360
Enough.

75
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,200
Stop arguing.

76
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,700
We all want the Crown Prince.

77
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,800
Since he's here,

78
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:55,990
handle the serious matter first.

79
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,240
Lady Chu is right.

80
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,750
Yun,

81
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,590
open the door.

82
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,520
How would I open it?

83
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,280
You need me to teach you?

84
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,590
Like this

85
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,240
and this.

86
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,360
Then it will open.

87
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:19,030
Go on, open it.

88
00:04:19,030 --> 00:04:19,910
Why don't you do it?

89
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:20,870
I'm not the Marquis of Zhenguo.

90
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:21,920
You do it.

91
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,720
I can't.

92
00:04:39,730 --> 00:04:41,120
You can, hurry.

93
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,840
Go on.

94
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,470
Come on.

95
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,400
Come on.

96
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,310
Stop it.

97
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:57,160
Come on, come on.

98
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,350
Who's there?

99
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,590
Your Highness!

100
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:07,560
Lady Chu is impressive.

101
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,000
- Greetings,
- Greetings,

102
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:19,360
Your Highness.

103
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,870
You barged into my room

104
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,470
without summons.

105
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,600
I could punish you for that, you know.

106
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,830
Oh, you dare?

107
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,070
Keeping a mistress in an inn,

108
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,150
you know it can't be seen.

109
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,790
Your are about to marry Tuantuan,

110
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:41,950
yet you do something

111
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:43,000
this disgraceful.

112
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:44,240
How are we supposed to

113
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,190
entrust Tuantuan to you?

114
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,720
As if your reputation outside

115
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,600
is spotless, Song Wenchang.

116
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:59,870
And I'm the Crown Prince.

117
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,160
I will have a harem in the future.

118
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,550
After the wedding,

119
00:06:03,570 --> 00:06:04,880
Qingping will be Crown Princess,

120
00:06:05,310 --> 00:06:06,360
and one day Empress.

121
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,270
Should an Empress

122
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,720
not tolerate other consorts?

123
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,720
Can you compare yourself to me?

124
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,540
I've never had a betrothal.

125
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,270
If I make a promise to a lady,

126
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,150
I would never be

127
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,010
as fickle as you.

128
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,800
Your Highness is correct.

129
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,680
Forcing our way into your quarters

130
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,600
is indeed a capital offense.

131
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:23,450
I will go to His Majesty now,

132
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:24,800
explain everything,

133
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,270
and accept punishment.

134
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,620
I as well.

135
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,250
I came today

136
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,250
by order of the Eldest Princess,

137
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,120
but forcing entry was improper.

138
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,510
I will

139
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:35,920
return and beg her

140
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,760
pardon.

141
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,440
But...

142
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,760
Right,

143
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,440
I'll inform my father and Tuantuan.

144
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,400
Stop.

145
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,750
Whatever you intend to do,

146
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,950
at least choose an appropriate place.

147
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,600
Hot wontons.

148
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,870
Her Highness used a pouch

149
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:08,950
to lead me to the inn,

150
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,310
she clearly knew what

151
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,680
the Crown Prince was doing.

152
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,680
But she's his aunt.

153
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,750
Why have me catch him in the act?

154
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,920
Wouldn't that harm the royal family's
reputation?

155
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,560
She is his aunt,

156
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:28,870
but compared to him,

157
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,310
she cares more about Lady Song

158
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,630
of the Duke of Hu's mansion,

159
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:32,560
Song Qingping.

160
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,840
This Lady Song

161
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,240
has long treated Her Highness's

162
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,120
chronic headaches

163
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,350
and helped her greatly.

164
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,120
So the Emperor betrothed her

165
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,960
to the Crown Prince.

166
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,040
Her Highness likely couldn't act openly,

167
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,070
so she had you run this errand.

168
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,190
First, to warn the Crown Prince

169
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,360
for her and Lady Song.

170
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,830
Second, to help our Wei family.

171
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,510
A plan that serves two sides,

172
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,430
clearly with Mr. Xue's touch.

173
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,350
But catching

174
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,480
the Crown Prince cheating

175
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,000
isn't exactly glorious.

176
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,880
You

177
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,680
won't spread this, right?

178
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,560
Do I look like someone who gossips?

179
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,590
If you don't

180
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,960
speak of it,

181
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,310
neither will I.

182
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,320
Good.

183
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:31,430
Looks like you won't need to worry

184
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,950
about tomorrow's banquet anymore.

185
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:51,420
(Marquis of Zhenguo's Mansion)

186
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:54,820
(True Might)

187
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:55,740
(Spirit tablet of Wei Sijie)

188
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:58,620
(Spirit tablet of Lady Qian)

189
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:04,020
(Spirit tablet of Lady Liu)

190
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:04,860
(Undying Loyalty)

191
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:05,700
Father,

192
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,230
Mother.

193
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:08,910
Whether I inherit

194
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:09,870
the title today or not,

195
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,240
as long as I live,

196
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,510
the Wei family will not fall.

197
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,870
I will carry the Wei name for you,

198
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:20,340
defend the nation and the throne,

199
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,480
hold no regrets.

200
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:52,660
(Ancestral Tablets of the Wei Clan)

201
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,020
(Marquis of Zhenguo's Mansion)

202
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,720
Uncle Yun,

203
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,000
who are we still waiting for?

204
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,440
Why aren't we eating?

205
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,320
So impatient.

206
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,360
Mother said many ladies

207
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,550
and gentlemen would come today.

208
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,030
But it's been two whole hours.

209
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,720
Did they get lost?

210
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,550
Uncle Yun,

211
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:08,240
should we go find them?

212
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,720
I am hungry.

213
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:13,350
Lingmo,

214
00:11:14,030 --> 00:11:15,630
didn't you just have snacks?

215
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,470
Hungry again?

216
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,960
Go play with your brother.

217
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:19,230
Let's eat.

218
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,110
Tell the kitchen

219
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,420
to bring the dishes to the hall.

220
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,840
We'll eat by ourselves.

221
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:39,060
(Defend the nation and the throne)

222
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,560
Yun,

223
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,960
I have an unreasonable request.

224
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,270
After today,

225
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,670
we're leaving the Wei Mansion.

226
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:04,750
Before we go,

227
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:07,480
I want to take one thing of Qin's

228
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,240
as remembrance.

229
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,080
Of course.

230
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,960
What would you

231
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:14,960
like to take?

232
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,510
When Wei Qin was alive,

233
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,270
his spear was his treasure,

234
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,790
full of his marks.

235
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,840
I want to take it.

236
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,800
Can I?

237
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,110
Han,

238
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,390
those spears

239
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:47,150
were forged by the seven

240
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,220
of them together.

241
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,870
Just leave them here,

242
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,880
it's like the brothers are reunited.

243
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,840
Yes.

244
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,150
Chun is right.

245
00:12:59,120 --> 00:12:59,960
No,

246
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,840
take it.

247
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:08,630
I can't bear to part with it,

248
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,200
but in the end,

249
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,240
it's only an object.

250
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,200
They

251
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,120
may never have the chance

252
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,960
to go to war again.

253
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:27,020
If seeing the spear

254
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:29,510
lets you remember your days

255
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,480
here with my brothers,

256
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,440
then that's the best use of them.

257
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:37,240
And my brothers

258
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:40,150
would surely be glad.

259
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:45,680
Yun,

260
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,440
thank you.

261
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,920
Alright.

262
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:09,600
Enough waiting.

263
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,440
Let's wait a bit longer.

264
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,040
Just a little bit.

265
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,040
Yes.

266
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,870
Maybe they're already at the gate.

267
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:18,150
Let's go check.

268
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,420
- Okay.
- Let's go.

269
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:22,030
Han, take the children

270
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,200
to the back garden.

271
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:24,720
Go on.

272
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,560
Let's go.

273
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,790
That day you insisted

274
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,200
on this banquet,

275
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,600
did you imagine this scene?

276
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,550
Whether they come is their choice;

277
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:43,150
whether we hold

278
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,440
the banquet is ours.

279
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:46,720
Do all we can, leave the rest to fate.

280
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,870
If you don't even dare try,

281
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:50,750
not even an immortal

282
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:51,870
could save you.

283
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,320
You personally delivered an invitation

284
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,160
to Her Highness.

285
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:57,200
And I invited the Crown Prince.

286
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,150
But look at the result.

287
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:03,480
We did our part,

288
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:06,000
but fate is decided.

289
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,920
Then

290
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,040
let's bet:

291
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,350
Obverse—

292
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:14,350
someone will come.

293
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,960
Reverses—no one will.

294
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:17,350
Dare you?

