410
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,590
This is the gift

411
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:31,960
I, Song Wenchang,

412
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:32,800
prepared for General Wei.

413
00:20:33,830 --> 00:20:35,000
Guess what's inside.

