00:21:58,790 --> 00:21:59,750
I wish you steadiness

456
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:00,590
and strength

457
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,000
as the Zhenguo Marquis.

458
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:09,670
Do you like it?

459
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:14,680
Today is a thank-you banquet.

460
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,920
Marquisate?

461
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,590
We waited half the day

462
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:19,920
