466
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:27,110
Who are you?

467
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,040
My sister.

468
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:34,720
So you're the famed

469
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,960
first beauty of Huajing,

470
00:22:36,350 --> 00:22:37,200
Lady Chu.

