00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:10,790
and loyal service,

489
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,270
the title of Marquis of Zhenguo

490
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,590
of the Great Sui,

491
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:17,360
grants him the Fish Tally,

492
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:20,310
and appoints him

493
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,130
Commander of

494
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,310
