509
00:25:21,110 --> 00:25:21,950
That's right.

510
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,790
You might lose your position

511
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,400
as the Crown Prince.

512
00:25:29,070 --> 00:25:30,920
