515
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:37,030
but you haven't inherited the throne yet.

516
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,550
Great Sui is still His Majesty's.

517
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,750
If you continue to favor civil over military,

518
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,160
once you inherit the throne...

519
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,590
Among the generals,

520
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,160
only the Wei clan

521
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,590
