00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,160
about General Wei going to Fragrance House

532
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,240
during his mourning period,

533
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,550
can this matter be dismissed?

534
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:30,960
As for the Marquis visiting

535
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,280
Fragrance House while in mourning,

536
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,630
His Majesty has investigated.

537
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:35,830
It was a misunderstanding.

538
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:38,550
It was...

539
00:26:43,470 --> 00:26:45,720
Mr. Song who

540
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:48,550
caused trouble there,

541
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:49,880
and the Marquis

542
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,310
