547
00:26:58,310 --> 00:26:59,150
Mr. Song,

548
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,590
isn't that right?

549
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:14,480
Yes.

550
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,830
Yes, of course.

551
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,760
